HffaHPStFIvRMSrpcFmEFDgMZ9awBtdCAzncUsyUsg.PNG.cookthedesign/Free_4_Fold_Leaflet_Mockup_2.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-f68b5cd5-2b16-4a12-81e8-de9430f60682\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-400508e6-75c3-4f25-a0fe-4d8758154a59\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDFfMjI4/MDAxNjY5ODcwNjQ3MDI3._X3DsScv80AcA7G6_lj_-RxmK3CP8CaMBIcPD2sSTpcg.PjDaXZ95tKSsVciIdzrsN64gR7bPcu8WcdlK9qTSUc0g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"828\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMDFfMjI4/MDAxNjY5ODcwNjQ3MDI3._X3DsScv80AcA7G6_lj_-RxmK3CP8CaMBIcPD2sSTpcg.PjDaXZ95tKSsVciIdzrsN64gR7bPcu8WcdlK9qTSUc0g.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c0cf9d86-79e2-4f11-bbe9-c696b3fe26fe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d9b36595-046f-44b7-97af-b453c8b21f9d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>4단 리플렛의 특징은 다음과 같습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b7fc685-40d2-4912-8af3-37eb54185a02\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d019475f-2d93-4114-b6a5-83f98ff4b0e5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">4단 리플렛은 8페이지로 구성이 되어 있어서 리플렛 종류중에 가장 많은 내용을 담을 수 있는 모양을 가지고 있습니다. 위 그림의 사이즈는 A3사이즈에서 한칸이 더 붙은 사이즈로 제작되었습니다. 이 사이즈는 국 장 3절 사이즈입니다. 국전지에 3개가 앉혀지는 효율적인 사이즈로 가장 일반적인 4단 리플렛의 사이즈입니다. 이 사이즈 외에도 작업은 가능하지만 종이의 출고 절수 (국전지 939mm × 636mm)에 맞춰 작업하시는것이 가장 효율적일 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f44a1177-d37d-4503-a043-4eef95cc1df8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8406602b-e962-4d63-8e38-99f7df515ffb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-ca1cb261-f497-4e2f-80c9-fa0c9136f195\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-161db054-3241-489f-ae01-9a72910f5f8d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fdfcb9f9-f105-445b-8a85-af6cc44f0185\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9bd07095-a769-4fd5-a75c-fa27cb017efb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-efde6f8e-d73f-4ec4-baa8-264afdbb265b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7ccd9bde-61db-41cf-9340-66598c4c2f87\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">전체사이즈 : 560mm × 297mm : 접은 후 1면 사이즈 : 140mm × 297mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-57d3c6ab-39f2-451e-9c82-d716a2d62e33\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-986f47be-f116-4eb6-bb98-918a6cc70880\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">여분 6mm 포함 사이즈 : 566mm × 303mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c667a332-e205-4eed-a33b-b49ed8a7d0cf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-70f73386-b298-48cb-985c-a1bb10b895e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8ba9024b-6a63-4939-a401-e3322f914824\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-99dc734a-3021-4996-ab2d-218f9d991c4c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee1b1d87-36f7-4825-954c-3e12bf1bee49\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4cdce990-f375-42e1-bfd3-8661c0589c3e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이는 다양한 종이를 선택하실 수 있습니다. 얇은 느낌의 종이에서 부터 두꺼운 종이까지 가능하십니다. 다만 바로 접으면 접히는 면이 터짐현상이 발생될 수 있습니다. 그래서 오시라는 후공정을 넣고 접는것이 기본입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fde8a635-ed58-41ac-a5e9-c0ab923c5a40\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f80da2ed-eed5-4f08-b983-ec73234582b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b0461423-203b-4038-834a-472f23e2e74f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3a7d2601-0ef4-4f41-a42b-11384ad8b323\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222898286189\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222898286189</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-525e45d9-4de9-4f26-a4e1-0453681d0730\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70bd7ce0-9d2a-4f9c-acea-36debc0e9054\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-be408d72-7108-412e-8ced-3b5ab96856b9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-265f0b8e-b392-409c-8d92-efd09128640e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-871fbb59-d7c1-4245-bef5-78d0e14b7a88\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7f848ad-383d-47ef-a9d2-8e35a560942c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-de3c9983-dec9-4300-a54d-78ce64f62c61\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">인쇄는 양면컬러가 기본입니다. 다만 요즘은 별색으로 처리하는 양면 2도 + 2도로 작업을 하실 수 있습니다. 다만 얼굴사진이 들어가고 컬로로 구현하는것이 조금도 제품의 퀄리티를 높일 수 있고 별색 2도와 컬러 4도의 가격차이가 크지 않은 만큼 4Color로 작업하시는 것을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17213ebd-9d3c-4e77-8167-a6aa47afaea6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-02bd2308-b800-4b4e-b7f7-ee5bdd373c27\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e64785ca-306f-4469-bf68-470d6ee8b451\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e6c09c6a-fa2d-432d-abae-527a01120ece\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본적으로 4단 리플렛은 오시 + 접지의 후공정을 가지고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0dde47b5-9a56-48ba-955e-77c196cf8e09\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-af112fb9-394b-4862-8549-e6e974c57276\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d918288-ba4b-429d-bd0f-c07ce5fa866a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-19276e7e-5d9f-49e5-a43a-679a887bf27c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ec2218f-74dc-4b71-9f62-44fa32c45811\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-64e2b682-ed5e-41eb-b37e-1d9164dcb2cf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>접지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c54348c8-3132-4ad8-864a-d65830f9604e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-968f4fb7-80e7-44d8-987a-28f96b448a7d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">4단 접지의 경우 다음 그림과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b7f28a7-2865-43a6-992e-9df522ad408c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-3b7f28a7-2865-43a6-992e-9df522ad408c\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMjBfMTc3/MDAxNjcxNTA0MjA1NTY0.g6zVkXVvzAKKcElqqCfThuHZIv_jMiYmE6BsHFZTuZ8g.v3rxpceMVDpoMGMKL4P3Kmic4r5KHcH48jGE3xKKUuMg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2832\", \"originalHeight\" : \"946\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMjBfMTc3/MDAxNjcxNTA0MjA1NTY0.g6zVkXVvzAKKcElqqCfThuHZIv_jMiYmE6BsHFZTuZ8g.v3rxpceMVDpoMGMKL4P3Kmic4r5KHcH48jGE3xKKUuMg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d48ae528-781f-4b74-b45e-16a496656cdf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4e8bbf29-1a12-4887-b135-4a1e574349e7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cb7790a1-fc4f-4ffd-8c21-012409c84a80\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">본 목업에 사용된 접지는 병풍접지타입입니다. 그 외에도 디자인과 용도에 따라 다양한 접지방법을 선택하실 수 있습니다. 다만 접지에 따라 디자인 제작시 접는 부분의 여분을 감안하여 디자인하는것이 포인트입니다. 접히는 부분에 여분을 1~2mm 더 여유있게 디자인하는것입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-60105c23-1092-488b-afde-5671857201a9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c0241813-2123-4560-ab02-9db26276c7d1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad919e12-78db-45c9-a4ab-cc03feb14bc0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7655c8da-dbc0-4b6d-a79c-ef2c80e583fb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 조금 더 나은 디자인감각과 가격경쟁력으로 고객에게 최선을 다할 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-182bdc28-72aa-4029-81bf-384d6ab39b03\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8ebbccc9-1402-4ec9-b175-a9f9eb41cb0f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96598636-8d93-4443-8b50-70f2fde11c38\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F222960756529#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
